Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.59,0:00:05.17,Default0,,0,0,0,,补考结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.88,0:00:07.68,Default0,,0,0,0,,考完了！我们考完了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:09.76,Default0,,0,0,0,,我觉得我不会被当
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.93,0:00:11.47,Default0,,0,0,0,,北原、今村
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.64,0:00:13.56,Default0,,0,0,0,,你们想去喝一杯吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.76,0:00:14.77,Default0,,0,0,0,,好啊，不赖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:15.93,Default0,,0,0,0,,好啊，我去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:18.23,Default0,,0,0,0,,太好了！北原，去你那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.39,0:00:19.85,Default0,,0,0,0,,对啊，去北原那里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:21.36,Default0,,0,0,0,,知道了，北原那里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.52,0:00:23.02,Default0,,0,0,0,,好，我带你们过去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:25.03,Default0,,0,0,0,,等一下好像有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.19,0:00:26.49,Default0,,0,0,0,,怎麽回事，北原？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.65,0:00:28.74,Default0,,0,0,0,,为什麽一定要去我那里？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:30.24,Default0,,0,0,0,,这还用说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:32.87,Default0,,0,0,0,,因为我们想检查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:34.70,Default0,,0,0,0,,检查？是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.87,0:00:37.08,Default0,,0,0,0,,今村之前也说过，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.46,0:00:39.58,Default0,,0,0,0,,我们又没有在一起！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.75,0:00:41.83,Default0,,0,0,0,,但你们住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.04,0:00:43.96,Default0,,0,0,0,,嘿，北原
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.13,0:00:46.21,Default0,,0,0,0,,这不是真的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.17,0:00:51.51,Default0,,0,0,0,,你不会真的跟古手川住在一起，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.68,0:00:53.43,Default0,,0,0,0,,如果他们发现，会杀了我！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.60,0:00:56.18,Default0,,0,0,0,,等一下他们已经认为我在跟千纱交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.35,0:00:58.14,Default0,,0,0,0,,真正的问题是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.31,0:01:03.15,Default0,,0,0,0,,如果他们发现我跟个像她这麽辣又漂亮的女生住在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.31,0:01:07.44,Default0,,0,0,0,,我无法想像他们会对我做出什麽事求你，耕平！救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.78,0:01:11.91,Default0,,0,0,0,,你这混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.95,0:01:16.79,Default0,,0,0,0,,热情点，朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.95,0:01:20.00,Default0,,0,0,0,,与阳光一同闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.16,0:01:23.50,Default0,,0,0,0,,纵入蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.67,0:01:27.46,Default0,,0,0,0,,一切都归夏天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.13,0:01:34.47,Default0,,0,0,0,,碧蓝之海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.69,0:01:45.48,Default0,,0,0,0,,热情点，朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:48.73,Default0,,0,0,0,,与阳光一同闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:52.03,Default0,,0,0,0,,纵入蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.24,0:01:56.20,Default0,,0,0,0,,一切都归夏天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:01:59.29,Default0,,0,0,0,,机会的拓展之海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:03.33,Default0,,0,0,0,,夏天是我们的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.50,0:02:07.00,Default0,,0,0,0,,我们向清澈的天空发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:10.13,Default0,,0,0,0,,夏天在我们手中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.30,0:02:14.22,Default0,,0,0,0,,热情点，朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.39,0:02:17.39,Default0,,0,0,0,,与阳光一同闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.56,0:02:20.85,Default0,,0,0,0,,纵入蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.06,0:02:24.48,Default0,,0,0,0,,一切都归夏天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:28.65,Default0,,0,0,0,,一颗快活的心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.82,0:02:31.65,Default0,,0,0,0,,别惹我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.82,0:02:35.16,Default0,,0,0,0,,就算你失败也要继续
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:39.03,Default0,,0,0,0,,一切都归夏天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:48.75,Default0,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来，伊织
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:49.96,Default0,,0,0,0,,奈奈华姊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:51.17,Default0,,0,0,0,,怎麽回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:53.88,Default0,,0,0,0,,大学的同学说今天要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:56.26,Default0,,0,0,0,,哇，你朋友要来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:02:58.30,Default0,,0,0,0,,麻烦你立刻躲起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:02:59.85,Default0,,0,0,0,,什麽？为什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:02.85,Default0,,0,0,0,,很难解释，老实告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:05.73,Default0,,0,0,0,,我生命有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:08.48,Default0,,0,0,0,,但他们不是你的朋友吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:11.36,Default0,,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.53,0:03:13.61,Default0,,0,0,0,,我带了酒跟点心来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:15.86,Default0,,0,0,0,,喔，谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:17.74,Default0,,0,0,0,,潜水商店？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.91,0:03:19.99,Default0,,0,0,0,,你住在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:21.62,Default0,,0,0,0,,店面不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.79,0:03:24.50,Default0,,0,0,0,,通常整间都是脏兮兮的裸男
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:27.04,Default0,,0,0,0,,我房间在另一边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.21,0:03:28.88,Default0,,0,0,0,,嘿，走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:31.21,Default0,,0,0,0,,你什麽意思？我要先看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.38,0:03:32.63,Default0,,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.34,0:03:36.26,Default0,,0,0,0,,我可以把千纱跟奈奈华姊藏在这一边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:40.89,Default0,,0,0,0,,这是我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:44.39,Default0,,0,0,0,,北原！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:46.64,Default0,,0,0,0,,小梓！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:49.31,Default0,,0,0,0,,你这混球！我太嫉妒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.48,0:03:50.90,Default0,,0,0,0,,我绝不会原谅你！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:52.73,Default0,,0,0,0,,这不是你们想的那样！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:55.03,Default0,,0,0,0,,喂，冷静点，各位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:56.53,Default0,,0,0,0,,山本？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:58.53,Default0,,0,0,0,,你要原谅这个叛徒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:04:00.20,Default0,,0,0,0,,他没有背叛我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:02.79,Default0,,0,0,0,,别为了个帽子这麽激动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:04.95,Default0,,0,0,0,,帽子？你打算戴上吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:08.17,Default0,,0,0,0,,他嫉妒到与现实脱离了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:10.17,Default0,,0,0,0,,这是什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:13.84,Default0,,0,0,0,,伊织！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:15.80,Default0,,0,0,0,,小蛋糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.01,0:04:17.05,Default0,,0,0,0,,这是栓剂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:18.26,Default0,,0,0,0,,这像吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:19.47,Default0,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.64,0:04:20.84,Default0,,0,0,0,,都是北原的错！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:22.30,Default0,,0,0,0,,我做错什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.68,0:04:26.56,Default0,,0,0,0,,这是我们社团玩游戏要用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:28.60,Default0,,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:31.15,Default0,,0,0,0,,这大小不是古手川的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:34.94,Default0,,0,0,0,,这太大了你这麽一说，的确很大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:37.78,Default0,,0,0,0,,一开始就不可能是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.95,0:04:41.24,Default0,,0,0,0,,如果是真的，脱下来的人就不可能回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:43.78,Default0,,0,0,0,,女孩子不会没穿胸罩就回家对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:46.12,Default0,,0,0,0,,她不是正常…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:48.83,Default0,,0,0,0,,这里没什麽可疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:54.59,Default0,,0,0,0,,我肯定是搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:00.22,Default0,,0,0,0,,怎麽了，各位？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:02.47,Default0,,0,0,0,,不！没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:04.76,Default0,,0,0,0,,这家伙的东西好诡异
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:07.56,Default0,,0,0,0,,我觉得他很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:10.60,Default0,,0,0,0,,我们假装没注意到好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:12.23,Default0,,0,0,0,,（《工作》）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:14.19,Default0,,0,0,0,,你想找工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:15.94,Default0,,0,0,0,,想存钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.11,0:05:18.99,Default0,,0,0,0,,潜水要花很多钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:20.61,Default0,,0,0,0,,（活动伴游）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:26.54,Default0,,0,0,0,,他是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:28.20,Default0,,0,0,0,,我们喝酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:31.50,Default0,,0,0,0,,是，喝酒然後忘记一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:33.88,Default0,,0,0,0,,想到就怕死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:36.42,Default0,,0,0,0,,你们究竟在说什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:39.38,Default0,,0,0,0,,恭喜补考通过！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:41.01,Default0,,0,0,0,,乾杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:48.31,Default0,,0,0,0,,啤酒放久会变苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:49.52,Default0,,0,0,0,,我知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:52.44,Default0,,0,0,0,,潜水後的第一口最棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:54.40,Default0,,0,0,0,,你说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:56.07,Default0,,0,0,0,,怎麽回事，山本？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:05:58.73,Default0,,0,0,0,,你在浴室超久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:00.19,Default0,,0,0,0,,喂，北原
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:02.70,Default0,,0,0,0,,怎麽了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:09.04,Default0,,0,0,0,,我碰到了天使
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:12.04,Default0,,0,0,0,,她好美！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:13.25,Default0,,0,0,0,,你在哪里看到她的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.42,0:06:15.88,Default0,,0,0,0,,我到外面呼吸新鲜空气她就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:17.09,Default0,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:21.05,Default0,,0,0,0,,我刚才看到她，我想…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:24.59,Default0,,0,0,0,,你想什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.76,0:06:27.18,Default0,,0,0,0,,我想跟她约会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:29.26,Default0,,0,0,0,,什麽？不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:30.93,Default0,,0,0,0,,你们根本不相配
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:34.73,Default0,,0,0,0,,我知道，但是…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:37.69,Default0,,0,0,0,,如果不可能那我要她帮我生孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:39.53,Default0,,0,0,0,,这家伙是个白痴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:41.53,Default0,,0,0,0,,光是承认认识他就觉得丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:44.11,Default0,,0,0,0,,我们很相似你也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:47.07,Default0,,0,0,0,,你要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:48.28,Default0,,0,0,0,,搭最後一班列车？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:50.12,Default0,,0,0,0,,我要去找那个天使
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:51.33,Default0,,0,0,0,,什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:52.83,Default0,,0,0,0,,你想要怎麽做？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:54.83,Default0,,0,0,0,,很明显，不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:57.08,Default0,,0,0,0,,我会跪下，求她跟我交往！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:59.34,Default0,,0,0,0,,要对一个女孩告白就是这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:02.26,Default0,,0,0,0,,现在我对你的过去很好奇了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:05.34,Default0,,0,0,0,,我回来时，就是个男人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:07.72,Default0,,0,0,0,,喔，真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:09.39,Default0,,0,0,0,,男人，是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:11.10,Default0,,0,0,0,,祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:14.35,Default0,,0,0,0,,你觉得会发生什麽事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:16.06,Default0,,0,0,0,,她很漂亮，所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:18.77,Default0,,0,0,0,,他会立即被拒绝然後放声大哭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.94,0:07:20.19,Default0,,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:22.86,Default0,,0,0,0,,我们不该打赌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:30.16,Default0,,0,0,0,,等一下，发生什麽事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.33,0:07:31.66,Default0,,0,0,0,,喂，北原！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:33.29,Default0,,0,0,0,,怎麽回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:34.87,Default0,,0,0,0,,你究竟怎麽了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:36.87,Default0,,0,0,0,,你这样还看不出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:39.29,Default0,,0,0,0,,你看得出来吗？不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:42.75,Default0,,0,0,0,,我刚才要去海滩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:46.55,Default0,,0,0,0,,结果碰到一群裸男
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.72,0:07:48.18,Default0,,0,0,0,,好，我了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:50.14,Default0,,0,0,0,,你说你了解是什麽意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.76,0:07:53.02,Default0,,0,0,0,,不确定，但肯定很可怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:55.85,Default0,,0,0,0,,看见裸男我的眼睛会烂掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:58.81,Default0,,0,0,0,,我们每天都看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:08:00.36,Default0,,0,0,0,,再来喝一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:02.82,Default0,,0,0,0,,反正你也会被拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:04.11,Default0,,0,0,0,,喝吧，忘掉这一切！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:06.40,Default0,,0,0,0,,你不可能交到女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:09.45,Default0,,0,0,0,,你们就不能安慰我一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:14.41,Default0,,0,0,0,,总之，检查过了北原没有跟古手川住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:15.58,Default0,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:16.79,Default0,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:18.42,Default0,,0,0,0,,你的笑话很烂，今村
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:20.29,Default0,,0,0,0,,不，我没开玩笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:24.17,Default0,,0,0,0,,耕平很爱说笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:27.34,Default0,,0,0,0,,我甚至不确定他们是否在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:28.76,Default0,,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:31.47,Default0,,0,0,0,,他有女朋友的话才奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:33.72,Default0,,0,0,0,,你们根本不了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:34.93,Default0,,0,0,0,,可爱的女孩才不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.10,0:08:37.73,Default0,,0,0,0,,伊织，我洗好澡了你可以去…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:44.94,Default0,,0,0,0,,抱歉！我不知道你有朋友在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:09:01.12,Default0,,0,0,0,,北原！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:04.29,Default0,,0,0,0,,不是！听我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:05.92,Default0,,0,0,0,,耕平，救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:08.51,Default0,,0,0,0,,地板别沾到血
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:11.30,Default0,,0,0,0,,你这混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.64,0:09:17.27,Default0,,0,0,0,,嘿，千纱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:18.48,Default0,,0,0,0,,怎麽了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:23.27,Default0,,0,0,0,,你看见我这样不觉得我很可怜吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:24.48,Default0,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.65,0:09:27.61,Default0,,0,0,0,,他的生命真的有危险…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:34.41,Default0,,0,0,0,,哇，这里的海洋好美！我想去！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:35.74,Default0,,0,0,0,,宫古岛，是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.91,0:09:37.70,Default0,,0,0,0,,我想去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:41.04,Default0,,0,0,0,,我想去那里潜水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.21,0:09:43.46,Default0,,0,0,0,,你们在讨论潜水？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:48.38,Default0,,0,0,0,,时田学长！我要尽快拿到证照去很多地方潜水！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.21,0:09:50.26,Default0,,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:53.30,Default0,,0,0,0,,很高兴看见你们对社团活动这麽热情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.47,0:09:55.72,Default0,,0,0,0,,我们今天要做什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:09:58.52,Default0,,0,0,0,,照你说的我带了宽松的衣服来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.02,0:10:01.06,Default0,,0,0,0,,我们要参加网球双打
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:02.52,Default0,,0,0,0,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:04.81,Default0,,0,0,0,,这是同伴默契训练的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:06.27,Default0,,0,0,0,,不是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.02,0:10:08.82,Default0,,0,0,0,,事实上，我们要的是奖金
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:11.65,Default0,,0,0,0,,奇妙仙子社长有个想法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:16.83,Default0,,0,0,0,,如果我们输，就把女子跟男子选美第二名的奖金给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:18.12,Default0,,0,0,0,,奇妙仙子？你是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:21.12,Default0,,0,0,0,,不可能用网球打败网球社吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:23.96,Default0,,0,0,0,,他们想要复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:26.13,Default0,,0,0,0,,想要羞辱我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:28.00,Default0,,0,0,0,,对，我知道那为什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.17,0:10:30.51,Default0,,0,0,0,,我们的结论是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:34.22,Default0,,0,0,0,,你的羞辱跟奖金比起来微不足道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:36.97,Default0,,0,0,0,,因为你们也没有什麽好损失的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:42.98,Default0,,0,0,0,,打击！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:46.19,Default0,,0,0,0,,这些人以为是来看棒球喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:48.98,Default0,,0,0,0,,连规则都不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:51.28,Default0,,0,0,0,,你们不打算加入吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:53.40,Default0,,0,0,0,,我从这里替他们加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:56.16,Default0,,0,0,0,,我也会尽力帮他们加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:10:58.45,Default0,,0,0,0,,你穿运动衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:11:00.33,Default0,,0,0,0,,怎麽不穿网球衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:03.58,Default0,,0,0,0,,要露腿，我会害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:05.83,Default0,,0,0,0,,但你在选美的时候穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:07.54,Default0,,0,0,0,,我当时有化妆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:09.38,Default0,,0,0,0,,而且我喝醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:11.71,Default0,,0,0,0,,〝化妆〞对你来说究竟代表什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:12.96,Default0,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:17.59,Default0,,0,0,0,,在那两位的旁边我没有信心穿成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:20.60,Default0,,0,0,0,,运动衣也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:23.68,Default0,,0,0,0,,是啊，穿网球装也只是更突出而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:25.98,Default0,,0,0,0,,反正我们也不是什麽网球高手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.65,0:11:29.98,Default0,,0,0,0,,（为小千纱准备的）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:32.07,Default0,,0,0,0,,今天，如同我们所同意的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:35.32,Default0,,0,0,0,,要打三场双打
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.49,0:11:37.70,Default0,,0,0,0,,好的我输也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:40.24,Default0,,0,0,0,,你今天没扮女装
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:41.45,Default0,,0,0,0,,你也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:42.87,Default0,,0,0,0,,我从没扮过！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.83,0:11:45.66,Default0,,0,0,0,,她是新人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:46.96,Default0,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:49.42,Default0,,0,0,0,,他以为他们没见过面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:53.59,Default0,,0,0,0,,她的妆像是盔甲保护她不受敌人攻打
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:55.76,Default0,,0,0,0,,第一场比试开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:58.84,Default0,,0,0,0,,时田学长！寿龙学长！加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:01.35,Default0,,0,0,0,,好的我会尽力的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:04.18,Default0,,0,0,0,,好的，一、二…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.56,0:12:08.31,Default0,,0,0,0,,15比0！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:12.69,Default0,,0,0,0,,刚才发生什麽事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:15.57,Default0,,0,0,0,,那个发球是怎麽回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.74,0:12:18.07,Default0,,0,0,0,,下次就没这麽幸运了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:23.03,Default0,,0,0,0,,非常好，寿龙！交给我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:24.20,Default0,,0,0,0,,不！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.41,0:12:25.41,Default0,,0,0,0,,接招！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:27.83,Default0,,0,0,0,,30比零！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:29.71,Default0,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:33.88,Default0,,0,0,0,,时田学长！寿龙学长！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:35.71,Default0,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:38.72,Default0,,0,0,0,,他们运动真的很强
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:43.18,Default0,,0,0,0,,其他人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:45.39,Default0,,0,0,0,,刚才还在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:48.14,Default0,,0,0,0,,也许喝多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:49.73,Default0,,0,0,0,,我去看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:51.73,Default0,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.23,0:12:54.11,Default0,,0,0,0,,这怎麽回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:56.94,Default0,,0,0,0,,他们真的喝醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.11,0:12:59.78,Default0,,0,0,0,,怎麽回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:03.28,Default0,,0,0,0,,喔，伊织、耕平！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:04.49,Default0,,0,0,0,,嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:06.54,Default0,,0,0,0,,这是怎麽回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:09.96,Default0,,0,0,0,,奇妙仙子拿酒给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:11.54,Default0,,0,0,0,,结果我们喝多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:15.84,Default0,,0,0,0,,还有酒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:18.51,Default0,,0,0,0,,他们根本没喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:22.22,Default0,,0,0,0,,瞬间蒸发？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.39,0:13:25.18,Default0,,0,0,0,,他们究竟给他们喝了什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:27.89,Default0,,0,0,0,,我们自己帮他们加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:29.06,Default0,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.23,0:13:30.94,Default0,,0,0,0,,比赛进行得如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:32.15,Default0,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.86,0:13:36.98,Default0,,0,0,0,,他的动作不太灵活了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:39.90,Default0,,0,0,0,,这两个也偷偷喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:43.41,Default0,,0,0,0,,这样的话，我们会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:46.33,Default0,,0,0,0,,我还以为他们会赢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:51.08,Default0,,0,0,0,,北原，有办法让他们清醒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:52.83,Default0,,0,0,0,,我有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:54.29,Default0,,0,0,0,,换边！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:57.38,Default0,,0,0,0,,这太简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.55,0:13:59.34,Default0,,0,0,0,,是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:04.18,Default0,,0,0,0,,这是什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:06.18,Default0,,0,0,0,,里面不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:11.94,Default0,,0,0,0,,躲猫猫社团获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:13.40,Default0,,0,0,0,,你们做了什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:14.77,Default0,,0,0,0,,我们逆转胜的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:18.07,Default0,,0,0,0,,与其让我们的队伍清醒不如让他们喝醉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.23,0:14:19.73,Default0,,0,0,0,,运动家精神呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.90,Default0,,0,0,0,,我们赢了一场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:24.78,Default0,,0,0,0,,该你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.95,0:14:27.08,Default0,,0,0,0,,去吧好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:31.37,Default0,,0,0,0,,对了，我的运动衣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.54,0:14:33.83,Default0,,0,0,0,,在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:37.42,Default0,,0,0,0,,我有不好的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.59,0:14:39.55,Default0,,0,0,0,,古手川，你网球厉害吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:40.71,Default0,,0,0,0,,还可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:41.97,Default0,,0,0,0,,哈罗，你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:44.18,Default0,,0,0,0,,你是选美比赛的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:45.76,Default0,,0,0,0,,我第二名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.93,0:14:49.26,Default0,,0,0,0,,你是古手川！靠裙子飞起来获胜！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.89,0:14:53.35,Default0,,0,0,0,,太可惜了！性感对我们没用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:57.86,Default0,,0,0,0,,你还是对着观众才让裙子飞起来好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:02.03,Default0,,0,0,0,,古手川？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:03.99,Default0,,0,0,0,,比赛开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:12.08,Default0,,0,0,0,,这是真正的比赛跟刚才不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:14.91,Default0,,0,0,0,,太没礼貌了！我们也很用心打
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:16.75,Default0,,0,0,0,,是的，喝点水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:18.50,Default0,,0,0,0,,加油，你们两个！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:22.13,Default0,,0,0,0,,千纱真的很认真
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.51,0:15:23.63,Default0,,0,0,0,,你！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:30.47,Default0,,0,0,0,,防得好！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.64,0:15:32.68,Default0,,0,0,0,,你们两个是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.31,0:15:37.60,Default0,,0,0,0,,我们加油吧！跟我喊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:38.94,Default0,,0,0,0,,千纱，NiceBody！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.11,0:15:40.36,Default0,,0,0,0,,NiceBody，古手川！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.52,0:15:42.11,Default0,,0,0,0,,NiceBody，小千！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.28,0:15:44.36,Default0,,0,0,0,,千纱，很厉害的NiceBody！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.53,0:15:46.45,Default0,,0,0,0,,我听到有人说有个女生身材很好！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:48.24,Default0,,0,0,0,,真的吗？在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:51.33,Default0,,0,0,0,,千纱！千纱！千纱！好样的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.49,0:15:53.83,Default0,,0,0,0,,停！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:57.00,Default0,,0,0,0,,计画改变，先打败弱的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.17,0:15:58.25,Default0,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:16:00.71,Default0,,0,0,0,,局数，二比零！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.51,0:16:06.63,Default0,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:08.80,Default0,,0,0,0,,喂！那太危险了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:10.97,Default0,,0,0,0,,她们瞄准身体在打
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:12.43,Default0,,0,0,0,,瞄准身体？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:15.52,Default0,,0,0,0,,就是针对对手的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:16.73,Default0,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:22.02,Default0,,0,0,0,,古手川，反击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:23.90,Default0,,0,0,0,,她也瞄准她们的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:25.90,Default0,,0,0,0,,好招！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:28.15,Default0,,0,0,0,,了解，那麽…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:29.36,Default0,,0,0,0,,千纱！NiceBody！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:30.62,Default0,,0,0,0,,NiceBody，古手川！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:33.37,Default0,,0,0,0,,小千纱，漂亮的NiceBody！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.54,0:16:35.04,Default0,,0,0,0,,是哪位？她在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:37.25,Default0,,0,0,0,,别喊了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:42.13,Default0,,0,0,0,,奇妙仙子获胜！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:44.63,Default0,,0,0,0,,怎麽了，千纱？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:47.26,Default0,,0,0,0,,你一直抓住裙子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:52.10,Default0,,0,0,0,,我要开始第三场比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:54.06,Default0,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:56.06,Default0,,0,0,0,,你的运动衣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:57.31,Default0,,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:17:00.77,Default0,,0,0,0,,不穿衣服就是他的运动服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.57,0:17:06.78,Default0,,0,0,0,,不知道结果会如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:09.90,Default0,,0,0,0,,我要修理这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:17.04,Default0,,0,0,0,,15比零！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.37,0:17:19.04,Default0,,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.88,0:17:26.55,Default0,,0,0,0,,30比零！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:29.22,Default0,,0,0,0,,不知道伊织这麽厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:32.39,Default0,,0,0,0,,他之前的球也控得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:35.05,Default0,,0,0,0,,是啊，他掀千纱的裙子时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:37.77,Default0,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:39.77,Default0,,0,0,0,,交给我吧除了游泳以外都行！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.69,0:17:42.19,Default0,,0,0,0,,你别太自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.35,0:17:43.56,Default0,,0,0,0,,来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:45.52,Default0,,0,0,0,,接招！你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:48.86,Default0,,0,0,0,,耕平！好！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.03,0:17:51.28,Default0,,0,0,0,,接招！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:03.25,Default0,,0,0,0,,北原，他们挺厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:05.67,Default0,,0,0,0,,是你太烂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:22.10,Default0,,0,0,0,,局数，四比零！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:23.85,Default0,,0,0,0,,这下糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:26.61,Default0,,0,0,0,,这样不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:28.98,Default0,,0,0,0,,是你不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:30.86,Default0,,0,0,0,,喔，对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.03,0:18:32.36,Default0,,0,0,0,,我忘记提了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:38.24,Default0,,0,0,0,,我们社团会录下比赛以便以後研究他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:39.99,Default0,,0,0,0,,什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:41.33,Default0,,0,0,0,,你这混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:43.67,Default0,,0,0,0,,你只想在我们输之後取笑我们！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:45.83,Default0,,0,0,0,,你输不输没关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:48.46,Default0,,0,0,0,,你穿成这样，我们早就笑死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:51.76,Default0,,0,0,0,,耕平，看来都到这步田地了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:53.34,Default0,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:56.26,Default0,,0,0,0,,没别的选择了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.43,0:18:57.85,Default0,,0,0,0,,生死一决吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:01.60,Default0,,0,0,0,,你们在计划什麽吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:04.60,Default0,,0,0,0,,当然没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.73,0:19:07.48,Default0,,0,0,0,,死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.98,0:19:11.78,Default0,,0,0,0,,那叫声是怎麽回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:14.28,Default0,,0,0,0,,太棒了，北原！漂亮的发球！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.45,0:19:16.53,Default0,,0,0,0,,就剩下稍做调整了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:18.16,Default0,,0,0,0,,这不是好的发球！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:21.62,Default0,,0,0,0,,没弹回来，而是直接挂网！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:23.37,Default0,,0,0,0,,小心！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:24.58,Default0,,0,0,0,,别躲，胆小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:25.87,Default0,,0,0,0,,谁是胆小鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.46,0:19:32.34,Default0,,0,0,0,,小心了，如果我躲，得分的就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.51,0:19:34.88,Default0,,0,0,0,,是，我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.09,0:19:39.68,Default0,,0,0,0,,不可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.73,0:19:47.10,Default0,,0,0,0,,他们并没有松懈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:48.77,Default0,,0,0,0,,社长！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.94,0:19:51.07,Default0,,0,0,0,,你受够了，对吧？投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:53.07,Default0,,0,0,0,,你这鲁蛇！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:55.40,Default0,,0,0,0,,我要打他或是摄影机！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:19:58.32,Default0,,0,0,0,,我们真的要对抗他们？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:19:59.57,Default0,,0,0,0,,都是你的错！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:03.33,Default0,,0,0,0,,我不在乎现在发生什麽事再用一次你的下流招数
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:07.04,Default0,,0,0,0,,现在是谁在说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.83,0:20:09.17,Default0,,0,0,0,,所以你不在乎我做什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.33,0:20:10.42,Default0,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:13.71,Default0,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.88,0:20:16.80,Default0,,0,0,0,,那我就瞄准一击定生死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.97,0:20:18.43,Default0,,0,0,0,,好，这才是我的北原！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:32.98,Default0,,0,0,0,,命中！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:36.40,Default0,,0,0,0,,你究竟想要…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.57,0:20:39.16,Default0,,0,0,0,,出了一点意外，一名选手出局
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:42.16,Default0,,0,0,0,,我们可以换选手，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.33,0:20:43.74,Default0,,0,0,0,,这是我加入的时候吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.91,0:20:45.37,Default0,,0,0,0,,我也可以打！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:52.50,Default0,,0,0,0,,（四比六，胜利！）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:56.59,Default0,,0,0,0,,看你搞的飞机，你这混球！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:20:59.30,Default0,,0,0,0,,你说你不管我做什麽的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.47,0:21:00.59,Default0,,0,0,0,,是针对他们，你这白痴！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:03.22,Default0,,0,0,0,,一点运动精神都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.39,0:21:05.89,Default0,,0,0,0,,他们赢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:08.69,Default0,,0,0,0,,伊织网球挺厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.85,0:21:10.73,Default0,,0,0,0,,你高中的时候打过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:12.90,Default0,,0,0,0,,是入学考试结束以後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.06,0:21:14.11,Default0,,0,0,0,,你没参加社团？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:15.32,Default0,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.69,0:21:18.82,Default0,,0,0,0,,我听说网球是在大学最容易交到女朋友的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:20.36,Default0,,0,0,0,,所以我跟朋友训练
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.53,0:21:21.53,Default0,,0,0,0,,太肤浅了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.70,0:21:23.37,Default0,,0,0,0,,你真是头脑简单
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:28.50,Default0,,0,0,0,,你不加入网球社可以吗？你这麽努力训练
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:29.79,Default0,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.96,0:21:32.00,Default0,,0,0,0,,我甚至没有机会选择
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.17,0:21:33.71,Default0,,0,0,0,,太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.88,0:21:35.67,Default0,,0,0,0,,伊织，你真是太不顺遂了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.84,0:21:38.51,Default0,,0,0,0,,你的记忆有毛病吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.67,0:21:41.13,Default0,,0,0,0,,总之，我打够网球了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:42.39,Default0,,0,0,0,,你确定？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.55,0:21:45.60,Default0,,0,0,0,,现在我有别的事情要做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:48.60,Default0,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.64,0:21:53.27,Default0,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.44,0:21:54.94,Default0,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.69,0:21:58.53,Default0,,0,0,0,,就这样，我们赢得奖金
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.69,0:22:00.28,Default0,,0,0,0,,来个过夜之旅吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:02.16,Default0,,0,0,0,,地点是冲绳岛！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:03.41,Default0,,0,0,0,,冲绳岛？冲绳岛？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.57,0:22:05.91,Default0,,0,0,0,,当真？当真？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.08,0:22:07.87,Default0,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.33,0:22:11.41,Default0,,0,0,0,,那是我们之前看的有关冲绳岛的杂志
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.79,0:22:15.17,Default0,,0,0,0,,他们是为了我们这麽做的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.33,0:22:17.25,Default0,,0,0,0,,冲绳岛，太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.42,0:22:18.88,Default0,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.42,0:22:26.30,Default0,,0,0,0,,（如何畅饮冲绳酒）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.31,0:22:28.39,Default0,,0,0,0,,（《碧蓝的尽头》水树夏夜）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.56,0:22:30.64,Default0,,0,0,0,,这是你的麦克风，北原
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.81,0:22:34.81,Default0,,0,0,0,,我也要…？好，来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.98,0:22:38.36,Default0,,0,0,0,,是，尽情唱你们似乎玩得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.98,0:22:45.99,Default0,,0,0,0,,童话在虚假的世界里低喃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.16,0:22:51.91,Default0,,0,0,0,,隐藏在完全黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.08,0:22:57.88,Default0,,0,0,0,,我最後几天伸向禁果
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.04,0:23:04.18,Default0,,0,0,0,,现在我知道了希望之歌的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.34,0:23:09.43,Default0,,0,0,0,,残破的装备再也不停止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.60,0:23:17.02,Default0,,0,0,0,,就算我将失去一切我也要让你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.19,0:23:23.11,Default0,,0,0,0,,困在遥远的天空我以折断的羽翼祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.32,0:23:29.08,Default0,,0,0,0,,因为我们一起跨越琶音的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.24,0:23:35.00,Default0,,0,0,0,,如果生命只对着共鸣之星的节奏闪烁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.16,0:23:38.00,Default0,,0,0,0,,我会牺牲一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.17,0:23:42.55,Default0,,0,0,0,,至死不渝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.76,0:23:44.76,Default0,,0,0,0,,乾杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.43,0:23:52.06,Default0,,0,0,0,,现在进广告！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.60,0:24:00.06,Default0,,0,0,0,,你是调酒师？太酷了！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.31,0:24:02.11,Default0,,0,0,0,,你们何不也试一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.32,0:24:03.82,Default0,,0,0,0,,你们穿起来挺帅的！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.32,0:24:07.49,Default0,,0,0,0,,我的眼睛！我的眼睛！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.70,0:24:09.37,Default0,,0,0,0,,我们是赤裸关系
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.53,0:24:11.87,Default0,,0,0,0,,（下一集《男人的鸡尾酒》）
